      "proposed_solution": null,
      "question": "<p>The attached drawings show both the pile layout and the final condition for the slope along the wharf at the North Wall.  The slope will need to be fully excavated and graded prior to driving pile.  Excavating and grading the slope is currently ongoing in this location.  The existing poles are in conflict with the final grading and crane access as shown in the attached drawings.  Please advise when these will be relocated.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
