      "question": "<p>Confirmation that the current working points provided by the Langan design on 3/12/26 are correct and that we can use them for construction. Attached is the design file they provided and the previous Working Point Table provided on 3/3/26. Below are the changes for Working Point 1 &amp; 23 given to us on 3/12/26. </p>\n<p> </p>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">WP_ID</span></strong></p>\n\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">X</span></strong></p>\n\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">Y</span></strong></p>\n\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">Z</span></strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">WP-1 (SW Corner)</span></p>\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">1458204.11'</span></p>\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">556896.23'</span></p>\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">-50.84</span></p>\n\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">WP-23 (SE Corner)</span></p>\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">1460171.79'</span></p>\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">556145.67'</span></p>\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">-50.84</span></p>",
