      "description": "<p>Please see the revised submittal for the bedding stone to be placed at the top of the slope at a depth of 12 inches. R4 riprap was selected for this material; however, due to conflicts with the piles, installation as a stone mattress is not recommended. Instead, the material will be placed on geotextile fabric as shown in the 90% Revetment Drawings. The geotextile and installation work plan will be submitted under separate future submittals. A letter from Vulcan confirming that the material is sourced from a virgin quarry and is free from environmental impacts is also attached. A subsequent submittal will address all materials supplied from this quarry.</p>",
