      "created_by_name": "Morris Donovan (Sparrows Point Container Terminal)",
      "description": "<p>During the SPCT weekly program coordination meeting it was identified that standardized daily report templates should be established in Procore.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Action:\n<ul>\n<li>Configure Procore Daily Log templates to define the information required from each contractor.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Items to consider include:\n<ul>\n<li>workforce reporting</li>\n<li>equipment usage</li>\n<li>work activities</li>\n<li>environmental monitoring</li>\n<li>safety observations</li>\n<li>key construction activities and constraints</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Purpose:\n<ul>\n<li>Ensure consistent daily reporting across contractors and improve visibility into site activities and progress.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Sent from Procore</p>",
      "distributions": "Conley Lew (AECOM), Frawley Connor (AECOM), Gase Jacob (AECOM), Gessner Mary (AECOM), Girandola Phillip (AECOM), Megna Eric (AECOM), Morris Donovan (Sparrows Point Container Terminal), Simpson David (AECOM)",
