      "created_by_name": "Morris Donovan (Sparrows Point Container Terminal)",
      "description": "<p>During the SPCT weekly program coordination meeting it was noted that three bathymetry surveys associated with dredging operations should be reconciled.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Action:\n<ul>\n<li>Review and reconcile the 3 available bathymetry survey datasets to confirm consistency of seabed profile and dredging quantities.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Purpose:\n<ul>\n<li>Ensure survey information used for dredging operations and quantity tracking is accurate and consistent.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Sent from Procore</p>",
