      "created_by_name": "Morris Donovan (Sparrows Point Container Terminal)",
      "description": "<p>During the SPCT weekly program coordination meeting it was identified that inspection coordination is required between Langan, Hilles and Allan Myers for DMCF construction activities.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Action:\n<ul>\n<li>Coordinate with Langan, Hilles and Allan Myers to determine key inspection hold points requiring Langan involvement.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Confirm:\n<ul>\n<li>inspection stages</li>\n<li>notification requirements</li>\n<li>required advance notice</li>\n<li>documentation and reporting procedures</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Purpose:\n<ul>\n<li>Ensure inspection activities are coordinated and integrated into the construction process to avoid delays or missed inspection requirements.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Sent from Procore</p>",
      "distributions": "Conley Lew (AECOM), Frawley Connor (AECOM), Gase Jacob (AECOM), Gessner Mary (AECOM), Girandola Phillip (AECOM), Megna Eric (AECOM), Morris Donovan (Sparrows Point Container Terminal), Simpson David (AECOM)",
