      "created_by_name": "Morris Donovan (Sparrows Point Container Terminal)",
      "description": "<p>During the SPCT weekly program coordination meeting the team discussed development of the program master schedule and identified the need to confirm next steps.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Action:\n<ul>\n<li>Confirm approach for development and management of the SPCT program master schedule.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Items to consider include:\n<ul>\n<li>schedule inputs from each contractor</li>\n<li>integration of project schedules</li>\n<li>schedule update and reporting process</li>\n<li>responsibility for maintaining the program master schedule</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Purpose:\n<ul>\n<li>Ensure a coordinated program-level schedule is established to support progress monitoring and program reporting.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Sent from Procore</p>",
      "distributions": "Conley Lew (AECOM), Frawley Connor (AECOM), Gase Jacob (AECOM), Gessner Mary (AECOM), Girandola Phillip (AECOM), Megna Eric (AECOM), Morris Donovan (Sparrows Point Container Terminal), Simpson David (AECOM)",
