      "created_by_name": "Morris Donovan (Sparrows Point Container Terminal)",
      "description": "<ul>\n<li>Requirement:\n<ul>\n<li>Ensure containment boom is installed and maintained for all waterside work.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Protocol:\n<ul>\n<li>REP and other contractors must immediately notify Phil in the event any sheen is observed on the water.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Purpose:\n<ul>\n<li>Ensure compliance with environmental protection requirements and rapid response to potential environmental incidents.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><em><strong>Note: This item will remain open for monitoring during marine construction activities.</strong></em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Sent from Procore</p>",
