      "description": "<ul>\n<li>Action:\n<ul>\n<li>REP to confirm the proposed Gut demucking &amp; Backfill plan approach including:<br />&bull; bench formation<br />&bull; material type and source<br />&bull; material placement methodology<br />&bull; compaction means and methods</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Purpose:<br />Ensure the proposed approach aligns with design intent and approved construction methodology prior to implementation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Sent from Procore</p>",
