      "created_by_name": "Morris Donovan (Sparrows Point Container Terminal)",
      "description": "<p>During the SPCT weekly program coordination meeting the team discussed the HH requirement associated with dredging operations and potential discharge options.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Items to evaluate include:\n<ul>\n<li>Whether HH capacity is required by 10/1</li>\n<li>Cost implications for Cashman if HH is not required</li>\n<li>Potential acceleration cost for Allan Myers to complete work by 10/1</li>\n<li>Feasibility of pumping dredged material into a partially completed DMCF</li>\n<li>Regulatory considerations including MDE, Dam Safety and Langan involvement</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Purpose:\n<ul>\n<li>Determine the most appropriate dredging discharge strategy and identify potential schedule or cost impacts to the program.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Sent from Procore</p>",
      "distributions": "Conley Lew (AECOM), Frawley Connor (AECOM), Gase Jacob (AECOM), Gessner Mary (AECOM), Girandola Phillip (AECOM), Megna Eric (AECOM), Morris Donovan (Sparrows Point Container Terminal), Simpson David (AECOM)",
